<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Sony Interactive Entertainment [5,122 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-interactive-entertainment">Sony Interactive Entertainment</a> and developers <a title="Companies > Insomniac Games [309 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-interactive-entertainment/insomniac-games">Insomniac Games</a> and Nixxes Software will release a free update for <em><a title="Games > Marvel's Spider-Man 2 [25 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/marvels-spider-man-2">Marvel’s Spider-Man 2</a></em> on July 28 that adds the new “Fresh Start Suit” inspired by the upcoming movie <em>Spider-Man: Brand New Day</em>, the companies <a href="https://twitter.com/PlayStation/status/2067321531668238637" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-1059739"></span></p><p><em>Marvel’s Spider-Man 2</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2651280/Marvels_SpiderMan_2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/marvels-spider-man-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>.</p><p>Watch the new trailer for <em>Spider-Man: Brand New Day</em> below.</p><h2><span><em>Spider-Man: Brand New Day</em> Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Spider-Man: Brand New Day - New Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6TnbSI4yfZY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
